com.facebook.buck.rules.macros

Class BuildTargetMacroExpander

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.macros.AbstractMacroExpander<BuildTarget>
      • com.facebook.buck.rules.macros.BuildTargetMacroExpander
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MacroExpander
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClasspathMacroExpander, ExecutableMacroExpander, LocationMacroExpander, MavenCoordinatesMacroExpander

    public abstract class BuildTargetMacroExpander
extends AbstractMacroExpander<BuildTarget>
    Abstract expander which resolves using a references to another BuildRule.

    Matches either a relative or fully-qualified build target wrapped in $(), unless the $ is preceded by a backslash.
